{"TopicId":161786,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Any mod for seeing CoM and CoL inflight?","CreatedByName":"juvilado","CreatedById":106978,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-08T09:00:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"juvilado","CreatedById":106978,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-08T09:00:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, i think this would be an invaluable tool for all of us, if we could see real time inflight \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECoM\u003C/abbr\u003E and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Lift\u0022\u003ECoL\u003C/abbr\u003E, is it possible?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheRagingIrishman","CreatedById":165004,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-08T13:42:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/149706-13-collide-o-scope-v115/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sarbian","CreatedById":57146,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-08T14:23:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/154834-130-anatid-robotics-mumech-mechjeb-autopilot-261-27-may-2017/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EMechjeb\u003C/a\u003E also does it, in the Attitude adjustment window\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"siimav","CreatedById":178033,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-09T18:25:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223084829\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161786\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496931829\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257146\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sarbian\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/8/2017 at 5:23 PM, sarbian said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/154834-130-anatid-robotics-mumech-mechjeb-autopilot-261-27-may-2017/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EMechjeb\u003C/a\u003E also does it, in the Attitude adjustment window\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf i remember correctly, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Mechjeb (mod)\u0022\u003EMJ\u003C/abbr\u003E doen\u0027t show \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Lift\u0022\u003ECoL\u003C/abbr\u003E when the vessel is outside the atmosphere. Not sure whether it\u0027s intended to be that way or just some limitation. Having both \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECoM\u003C/abbr\u003E and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Lift\u0022\u003ECoL\u003C/abbr\u003E visible in space would allow to re-balance fuel before reentry to make the vessel perfectly stable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-11T03:43:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes it does show \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Lift\u0022\u003ECoL\u003C/abbr\u003E outside of atmosphere.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}